INSERT INTO `ys_article` VALUES ('1', '澳洲11日（悉尼-墨尔本-凯恩斯）衣食住行攻略全记录', '<p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">这是我到目前为止写的最费劲的攻略了~~之前写的一般都是4-5日的攻略，日本也就7Days而已，这个行程一共11Days，城市涵盖了<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/sydney236.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1743636_236_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"236\" data-id=\"152\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">悉尼</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/melbourne312/136496.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1743636_312_sii136496_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"136496\" data-id=\"98058\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">墨尔本</a>还有<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/cairns453/136484.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1743636_453_sii136484_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"136484\" data-id=\"98047\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">凯恩斯</a>及道格拉斯，东西多的一塌糊涂，555555555</p><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">这里先介绍一下澳大利亚吧，首先这是一个移民大国，在大英帝国没有踏上这块领土之前，这里全是一些无忧无虑生活的非常happy的土著，自从库克船长发现了这块富饶的土地之后，土著们的噩梦就来了，西方侵略势力大肆屠杀土著人民并且把这里占为己有。原先这块土地好像就是英国的囚犯聚集地，不知道什么原因，开始大量接受各国的移民，最大规模接受中国移民貌似就是在1989年天安门事变的时候。另外因为澳大利亚接受全球的政治难民，因此~~~赖某某才能在这里度过那么多年~~~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">还有比较好玩的地方就是澳大利亚出名的城市大家都知道是悉尼和墨尔本，但是首都呢，<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/canberra321.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1743636_321_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"321\" data-id=\"217\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">堪培拉</a>，非常年轻的城市，有它的原因就是因为澳大利亚的首都迟迟定不下来，原因呢，当然就是悉尼人民和墨尔本人民掐架咯....所以，最终决定在悉尼和墨尔本之间成立了这么个首都，怎么有种傀儡的赶脚~~~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">澳大利亚有6个洲，每个州都有独立的立法权，甚至可以规定自己的时间（这个尤为重要，大家不要因为看错时间导致飞机航班延误哟）！！！所以~~~悉尼(<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/newsouthwales25025.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1743636_25025_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"25025\" data-id=\"23043\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">新南威尔士州</a>)和墨尔本（<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/victoria25027.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1743636_25027_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"25027\" data-id=\"23045\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">维多利亚州</a>）跟中国有3小时时差，而凯恩斯所在的<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/queensland25026.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1743636_25026_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"25026\" data-id=\"23044\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">昆士兰州</a>跟国内只有2个小时的时差，据说有个洲还存在0.5小时的时差，小伙伴们凌乱呀...P.S.而且澳大利亚有几个洲还是有夏时令的呢，现在还存在夏时令的国度可是不多的哟~~~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">至于到了这边之后呢，留下了几个非常深刻的印象，哈哈哈:</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">1.气候多变</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">大家都说澳大利亚过的是夏天，但是我们过去的时候真心觉得冷呢，一点都没比杭州暖和，气候多变得一塌糊涂，去的朋友们请自带一年四季的衣物....早晨和傍晚气温骤降，外加上风很大，所以风衣必备！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">中午太阳出来的收又热到不行~~有点像大连的冬天，哈哈哈</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">所以穿的就很怪异~~~当然老外穿什么的都有~~背心跟羽绒服经常同时出现~~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img11864931\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"11864931|1743636\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"11864931\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"11864931|2933238\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/581/325/196/8124102671334d768a93346932707e7b_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/581/325/196/8124102671334d768a93346932707e7b_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/581/325/196/8124102671334d768a93346932707e7b_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"447\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">2.物价超贵</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">去过那么多国家，就算是迪拜日本吧...也没这么贵呀~~5555555我到了新加坡迪拜水也就只要1美金吧....这里都是2-3刀的，阿门；我怕到日本一顿饭也就人均100吧...这里人均600的都吃到了....阿门~~简直贵到了天花板，澳洲的小伙伴们到底是怎么活过来的~~~（当然也有便宜的，比如奶粉和鱼肝油，小伙伴们惊呼便宜到了地下室....）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img11865082\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"11865082|1743636\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"11865082\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"11865082|2933238\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/549/611/347/bf9b07ea311c4d059a1db220419f512b_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/549/611/347/bf9b07ea311c4d059a1db220419f512b_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/549/611/347/bf9b07ea311c4d059a1db220419f512b_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">3.动物天堂</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">在大阪每天都能看到乌鸦，到了悉尼每天看到的是海鸥，叫的差不多，无法分辨，据说很凶，会啄人....</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img11865083\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"11865083|1743636\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"11865083\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"11865083|2933238\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/334/307/686/58b3f5c8d9a84a089992d664cdc94173_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/334/307/686/58b3f5c8d9a84a089992d664cdc94173_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/334/307/686/58b3f5c8d9a84a089992d664cdc94173_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">另外街道两旁的树上仔细看看你会发现抱着大树昏昏欲睡或者是睡到不知道白天黑夜的考拉~~~话说大家知道考拉是怎么死的吗~~据说是老了抱不动树..所以~~~天上掉下个考拉拉....摔死了~~~(太高了....对焦没对好~~)</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img11865084\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"11865084|1743636\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"11865084\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"11