，俯看这庞大的拉美西斯二世雕像，感觉这尊石像的雕琢非常的精致，虽说经历了三千多年的岁月，但是雕像上面的象形文字还是依稀可见的。拉美西斯二世雕像的双脚和左手是残缺的，据说是由于一场地震。</p><p class=\"poi_name\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"https://you.ctrip.com/sight/cairo326/13195.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span class=\"sight\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 16px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin-right: 5px; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;) -249px 0px no-repeat;\"></span>孟菲斯博物馆<span class=\"decoration_arr\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 6px; height: 16px; vertical-align: top; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/w_travels.png?t=e01e377055e80d92c52b9260e20c49ba&quot;) -330px -16px no-repeat;\"></span></a></p></div></div><div class=\"img_box\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 850px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><div id=\"img11744636\" class=\"w_img \" data-likeid=\"11744636|1737250\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"11744636\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"11744636|9110875\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: auto; overflow: hidden; max-width: 850px;\"><a class=\"al\" share-pic=\"1\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/tg/190/934/619/e2127975d491480688a89de38085de7b_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225); display: block; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"><img data-original=\"https://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/tg/190/934/619/e2127975d491480688a89de38085de7b_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" src=\"https://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/tg/190/934/619/e2127975d491480688a89de38085de7b_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" height=\"466\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 850px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; max-height: 600px;\"/></a><p class=\"description\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">公元前3100前传说中的埃及法老美尼斯统一了上下埃及，并在尼罗河三角洲与山谷的交汇处建立了孟菲斯，也就是说，这些散落的石刻已经在风雨侵蚀中存在了5000多年。</p></div></div><p><br/></p>', '7', '6', '2', '2018-05-27', '2019-06-02T12:10:50+', '已发布', '\\uploads\\1559448640360-f508887f90f84d18b9f681b52f50648b_C_210_140.jpg', '回过头，瞠目结舌地望着吉萨金字塔，你一生中应该去的地方又完成了一个。 ——《Lonely Planet Egypt》 如果非要问我选择埃及的理由，我想这个答案应该足够充分。有人说，古埃及人建造金字塔陵墓，不是基于死亡带来的困扰，相反，是出于他们对于永生的坚定信念和希望与宇宙融为一体的强烈欲望。', '979', '5', '1');
INSERT INTO `ys_article` VALUES ('9', '【加游站】【南半球不孤单】上天入海与父母同乐，记迟来的澳新精', '<p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">那啥，先解释一下题目。为什么叫迟到的旅行呢？因为贝勒哥曾在<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/australia100048.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_2139846_100048_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"100048\" data-id=\"58750\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">澳大利亚</a>念书，本来毕业时想接父母来耍一圈的，结果由于种种原因未能成行。如今归国已六载，眼看父母年事渐高白发及鬓，这迟迟未了的夙愿必须得抓紧了。于是贝勒哥和小P分别以N寸不烂之舌说服了领导请下年假（吐槽：苦13上班族每年5天年假真心伤不起啊，你们懂的），再加上国庆和周末一共凑了15、6天，然后就开始规划行程、办理签证等等。话说，其实这次出行在确定目的地方面没费太大力气，毕竟澳大利亚是除了中国以外哥最熟悉的地方了，新西兰也曾去过一次，算是故地重游。<br/><br/>老实说，十几天的时间对于大洋洲这两个旅游BOSS国来说任选其一都远远不够，但考虑到我们未来假期的不确定性和超长难熬的飞行时间，父母们最终还是一致决定挑重点把两个国家一锅儿端了。考虑到澳大利亚和新西兰以自然风光闻名于世，这一趟注定是重自然轻人文。简单规划后，定下了主游<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/melbourne312/45089.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_2139846_312_sii45089_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"45089\" data-id=\"82228\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">大洋路</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/cairns453/22951.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_2139846_453_sii22951_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"22951\" data-id=\"81297\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">大堡礁</a>以及新西兰南岛，抽零碎时间顺带逛<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/melbourne312/136496.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_2139846_312_sii136496_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"136496\" data-id=\"98058\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">墨尔本</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/sydney236.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_2139846_236_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"236\" data-id=\"152\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">悉尼</a>的行程。<br/><br/>自打行程敲定，就开始琢磨怎么痛玩，回来怎么更新游记，可真到要写，却又找不到好的提笔思路。想来一是因为澳新两地贝勒哥都已去过，这次走经典路线总体上没有过多出乎意料的惊喜；二是虽然计划让父母们过个休闲安逸的假期，但最终还是贪多把行程安排的稍嫌紧凑，一路上虽不算来去匆匆，但多少也留了点儿遗憾。唉，总是渴望一趟华丽丽的旅程，把这里那里的风景名胜美食人文一路全包，却忽视了有取有舍的不完美也许才是旅行最真的一面，毕竟人的精力、时间还有金钱都那么有限。<br/><br/>思来想去玩不出什么花样，咱就还是老套路按地点流水账吧。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img20187691\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"20187691|2139846\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"20187691\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"20187691|13993356\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/995/180/505/653bdd7abc254552aa93e6e107d96f32_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/995/180/505/653bdd7abc254552aa93e6e107d96f32_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/995/180/505/653bdd7abc254552aa93e6e107d96f32_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"650\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong>交友启示（我能告诉你这其实是赤果果的广告么？）</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">各位爱玩爱跑爱拍爱摄的兄弟姐妹，如果你喜欢贝勒哥的图文，请关注偶，还有偶的其它游记（北欧、大马、新加坡、肯尼亚、马尔代夫，后面陆续还有新西兰北极光神马的），最好再猛戳一下贝勒哥微博：@木彡贝勒，以及博客 / Lofter：木彡贝勒。严重欢迎各位无级、初级、中级、高级还有骨灰级驴友灌水拍砖。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img20187735\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"20187735|2139846\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"20187735\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"20187735|13993356\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/876/149/448/632bf2d9aa8c43ad88bbb44d218eba54_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/876/149/448/632bf2d9aa8c43ad88bbb44d218eba54_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/876/149/448/632bf2d9aa8c43ad88bbb44d218eba54_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"650\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">猥琐的发完广告，正文走起。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong>目录：</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong>前言&amp;行前</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong>Chapter 1：重返墨尔本，那些年我们一起写论文的地方</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong>Chapter 2：最美沿海公路——大洋之路</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bo