0000up1f1516A_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">房间里的细节还是挺棒的，有带热屁屁的马桶，还有地暖，第二天我们去&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/fuyang1513.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3796774_1513_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"1513\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">富阳</a>&nbsp;下雨鞋子和油纸伞都湿了，放在地暖上一晚上都干了，真是地暖妙用哈哈哈哈。</p><div id=\"img311844079\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"311844079|3796774\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"311844079\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"311844079|50916868\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100o13000000uctzzC20F_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100o13000000uctzzC20F_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100o13000000uctzzC20F_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">房间视野特别好，民宿处在半山腰上，可以看到周边的群山，旁边的一棵 大树 在春天里发了新芽，在阳光下熠熠发光，春天呀，触手可及。</p><div id=\"img311844156\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"311844156|3796774\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"311844156\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"311844156|50916868\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100l13000000ue5nk2E41_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100l13000000ue5nk2E41_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100l13000000ue5nk2E41_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">另外给大家普及一下关于“西湖风景区”的知识点。对于我们这种外地人来说，西湖就是西湖，来 杭州 也只知道西湖，但是实际上“西湖风景名胜区”是一个很大的区域，在地图里西 湖西 南方向是一片超大的绿色，在这里是被精心保护起来的城中森林，有<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/hangzhou14/2040.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3796774_14_sid2040_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"2040\" data-id=\"75771\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">灵隐寺</a>、 龙井 博物馆、云栖竹径等藏在深山里的美丽景色，也散落着大大小小的酒店民宿，这几天的行程里我们也大都在西湖风景区里活动，晚上开车还真的有在深山老林里的感觉，也真的是很神奇的体验。</p><div id=\"img311843829\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"311843829|3796774\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"311843829\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"311843829|50916868\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100s13000000ukvb86441_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100s13000000ukvb86441_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100s13000000ukvb86441_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: