"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">有一种感觉，OCTO Seafood餐厅就像一个航空母舰，舰艇上各国餐饮百花齐放。</p><div id=\"img304631847\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"304631847|3768940\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"304631847\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"304631847|2361425\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100v10000000pesyv2D44_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100v10000000pesyv2D44_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100v10000000pesyv2D44_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">明明在同一个屋檐下，走两步却能感受到不同国家的文化氛围。而总有一款美食能满足你的味蕾。时尚潮流人士更愿意把这里当做可以品尝美食、美酒和享受音乐的新社交天地。</p><div id=\"img304631848\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"304631848|3768940\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"304631848\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"304631848|2361425\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100k10000000p7xqy47F8_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100k10000000p7xqy47F8_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100k10000000p7xqy47F8_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">如果你想要得到更多惊喜，一定要等到晚上。那时候整个餐厅穹顶会投影出动态的海底世界，超震撼。还有DJ打碟，用Groove Music style开场，营造了浪漫的气氛，仿佛海底漫游。</p><div id=\"img304631679\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"304631679|3768940\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"304631679\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"304631679|2361425\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100210000000pau4q77F7_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100210000000pau4q77F7_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100210000000pau4q77F7_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">菜品方面:招牌咸蛋鱿鱼很赞,咸蛋提味与鱿鱼鲜味结合完美。个人还喜欢八爪鱼脚刺身，他们下面铺垫的居然是水果粒，番茄粒还有牛油果，棒棒哒。<br/></p><div id=\"img304631680\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"304631680|3768940\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"304631680\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"304631680|2361425\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100m10000000pd53b1CEE_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100m10000000pd53b1CEE_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100m10000000pd53b1CEE_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">龙虾就不用说了，个大鲜美，饱满的虾肉上面还有猪肉沫超级好吃。挤点柠檬，味道更是恰到好处。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img304631932\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"304631932|3768940\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"304631932\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"304631932|2361425\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100m10000000pd53fDD6A_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100m10000000pd53fDD6A_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100m10000000pd53fDD6A_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">我们还点了西餐区的火腿披萨，意大利的火腿片真好吃。炸大鲈鱼则是<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/restaurant/thailand100021.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3768940_100021_l\" data-classtype=\"0\" data-resourceid=\"100021\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"9\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">泰国餐厅</a>必点菜式，超丰盛。生蚝配不同酱汁味道大不相同。而且他们生蚝品种很多，可以点不同品种来品尝。</p><div id=\"img304631682\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"304631682|3768940\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"304631682\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"304631682|2361425\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100s10000000pamum8B4C_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100s10000000pamum8B4C_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100s10000000pamum8B4C_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">这是店里的日料区，也是相当可爱逗趣。很有风格个性，铁板烧后面的手绘墙也是相当有看头。</p><div id=\"img304631683\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"304631683|3768940\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"304631683\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"304631683|2361425\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100310000000p5hh055D2_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100310000000p5hh055D2_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100310000000p5hh055D2_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">去的那天碰上楼上品酒活动，小伙伴就带我上楼玩了下，上图左上就是打碟DJ，品酒会有各种白葡萄酒、红酒和香槟，感觉到泰国人还是很会享受生活的。</p><div id=\"img304631933\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"304631933|3768940\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"304631933\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"304631933|2361425\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100i10000000p2kqd3DCA_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100i10000000p2kqd3DCA_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100i10000000p2kqd3DCA_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">二楼的Dr. Fetch有现场乐队和Hip Hop DJ,还会演奏Old School类型的音乐，酒吧里的鸡尾酒也很特别，我点的这个虹吸壶就很适合女性。<br/>地址：Octo Seafood Bar, 88/22 Sukhumvit Soi 24, Bangkok, Thailand</p><p><br/></p>', '26', '2', '4', '2019-05-14', '2019-06-02T12:39:12+', '已发布', '\\uploads\\1559450340779-t.jpg', '写在前面的话作为一个去泰国七次的人，很惊喜每次去都有新发现新收获。我想这就是我一直步履不停的原因吧。这次12月中旬刚去的泰国，是受泰国小伙伴邀请，所以每一天都是不用做攻略的快活日子，每一天都在我圆梦增肥的路上大快朵颐，每一天都忍不住想要买买买。好了，不能我一个人这样子，新年春节快到了，送上这个刚新鲜出炉的攻略给你们，祝大家2019旅途愉快。我的微博：@Abby45, 微信公众号：不旅不婷，欢迎来交', '1232', '3', '1');
INSERT INTO `ys_article` VALUES ('21', '自驾西澳，2000公里的路和云，跨过山和大海，只为遇见你', '<p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">感觉所有的文字所有的照片都显的如此苍白无力，一直在思考该用怎样的标题来体现出它的灵魂之美，美到让人窒息，幻境中呈现，或许不过弹指挥间，怎敌你早已占据心尖，挥之不去，断长眠……</p><div id=\"img313247117\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"313247117|3801652\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"313247117\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"313247117|20561754\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100313000000vogi32179_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100313000000vogi32179_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100313000000vogi32179_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">你也许走过很多地方，也许看过不同的海，从北冰洋的常年冰寒到南太平洋的温暖湿润，但心里总会藏着一片海，来了就舍不得走，今天的你或许正坐在办公室前做着PPT，或正坐在沙发上看着电视，亦或是在异国他乡求学，那就让小娴带你听听印度洋的海浪，看看西澳的大海吧……</p><div id=\"img313247276\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"313247276|3801652\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"313247276\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"313247276|20561754\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100t13000000vms1352F5_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100t13000000vms1352F5_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100t13000000vms1352F5_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">这次来到的是被称为“世界上最孤独的城市”——珀斯，西面是浩瀚的印度洋，东面是澳大利亚内陆地区，因为它离世界上任何一个大城市都很远，同时人口稀疏，而令人惊喜的是，《妻子的浪漫旅行 第二季》的其中一个目的地就选在了这里，珀斯当地最大的媒体《The West Austrlian》报纸和网站的头版头条都亮了！！！</p><div id=\"img313247210\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"313247210|3801652\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"313247210\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"313247210|20561754\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100w13000000vsrirA1D7_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100w13000000vsrirA1D7_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100w13000000vsrirA1D7_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">绝大部分国内的游客去澳洲都会去悉尼、墨尔本、黄金海岸、大堡礁、塔斯马尼亚等，只有极少数的游客才会去西澳，但就整个澳洲的旅行资源而言，西澳一点都不会输给澳洲的其他城市，在这片大地上，有蓝色、白色、红色、黄色、粉色……从未有一片大地拥有如此丰富的颜色，像是上帝的抽象艺术品。</p><div id=\"img313247467\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"313247467|3801652\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"313247467\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"313247467|20561754\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/t