un, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100d14000000vnt6iD006_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100d14000000vnt6iD006_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100d14000000vnt6iD006_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">今年和夏天算是彻底扛上了，冬天在我的印象里似乎只是一个过客，冬季的江浙沪就如同冰柜一般让人待不下去，于是整个冬天几乎都是在热带度过的，从印尼到泰国再到三亚……</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">而在春节期间，也停止不了爱旅行的脚步，和一群从未见过面的陌生人相约一起去了澳洲，而旅行永远有一个特殊的磁场，它把同行的人放到一个完全陌生的环境中朝夕相处，把平常隐藏的脾性和习惯全部暴露出来并加以放大，它可以使得原本生活中很好的朋友旅行归来如同陌生人，也能让原本不认识的陌生人旅行归来就成为了好朋友，磁场相吸的人终会相遇，旅途中的那一张张笑脸至今都深深印在我脑海中……</p><div id=\"img313247374\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"313247374|3801652\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"313247374\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"313247374|20561754\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100414000000vo9ua163D_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100414000000vo9ua163D_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100414000000vo9ua163D_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p><br/></p>', '26', '5', '2,3,4', '2019-05-14', null, '已发布', '\\uploads\\1557836983252-100313000000vogi32179.jpg', '趴在电脑前，单曲循环着《Skinny love》，这是自驾西澳途中车里放的次数最多的一首歌，由于当时我们三的手机里下载的歌曲并不多，所以反复听了好多遍，印象中每当我朦胧中醒来就是这首歌，当时听得无比腻强烈要求切歌，而如今听来脑海里都是一路的欢声笑语，记忆里的画面一下子浮现了出来，原来真的有那么多歌曲能让人想起很多情境来。', '114', '7', '1');
INSERT INTO `ys_article` VALUES ('22', '左手温柔，右手惊艳，人生无憾——非洲津巴布韦、纳米比亚、南非', '<p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">人生那么短，如果不能做喜欢的事，宁愿不活。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">人生那么短，如不能和喜欢的人过日子，宁愿不爱。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">写游记的意义，是什么？炫耀，显摆？坦白讲，确实有点哈，虚荣心是人之常情。但认真写过游记的人，都那么刻苦铭心地劳累过，几千张堆积如山的照片，一大团像乱线毛线球挤在一起的途中记忆。如果一个男的有耐心娓娓道来，必是耐心之人，可考虑投寄终身幸福了啊。我的动力更多是，在回顾梳理清全程同时，重新发现和补充在途中未知的新知识。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">旅行的意义，是什么？我想，不是路上有多少惊艳的美景或美食，更多的是，面对各种奇葩紧急事情时，充盈内心的淡定。最重要是，确信生命中永远存在另一种可能性，生活再残酷也能找到希望的出口。</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">全文的叙述方式是先文字加图片情绪激昂感慨一番——后穿插上基本攻略和注意事项，尽量做到文字图片加攻略的完整结合。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">为能顺利出行，苦苦等了一个半月，一个国家2星期的签证，花掉6星期。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">出行前一直安慰自己，从所未见的壮观景色，会让所有等待都值得，就如心爱人值得静候般。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">@行程安排：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day1 6月23日香港/<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/johannesburg328/136756.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1892110_328_sii136756_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"136756\" data-id=\"98255\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">约翰内斯堡</a>/<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/fallscity143893.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1892110_143893_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"143893\" data-id=\"10551507\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">瀑布城</a>（<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/zimbabwe100150.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1892110_100150_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"100150\" data-id=\"58837\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">津巴布韦</a>）参考航班：SA287 HKGJNB 2355 0700+1</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day2 瀑布城参考航班：BA6285 JNBVFA 1125 1305</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day3 瀑布城/<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/windhoek19988.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1892110_19988_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"19988\" data-id=\"18456\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">温得和克</a>（<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/namibia100151.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1892110_100151_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"100151\" data-id=\"58838\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">纳米比亚</a>）参考航班：SW403 VFAWDH 1230 1310</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day4 温得和克—苏丝斯黎沙丘（车程约365公里，约5小时30分）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day5 苏丝斯黎沙丘</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day6 苏丝斯黎沙丘—斯瓦科普蒙德（车程约400公里，约5小时）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day7 斯瓦科普蒙德—鲸湾—斯瓦科普蒙德（单程车程约35公里，约30分钟）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day8 斯瓦科普蒙德-十字角-卡曼杰布（车程约450公里，约6.5小时）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day9 达玛拉兰地—辛巴部落（车程约100公里，约1.5小时）—埃托沙（车程约250公里，约3小时）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day10 埃托沙</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day11 埃托沙—温德和克（车程约460KM，车程约6小时）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day12 温德和克/<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/capetown327.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1892110_327_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"327\" data-id=\"222\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">开普敦</a>参考航班：SW709 FR04JUL WDHCPT 1635 1935</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day13 开普敦</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day14 开普敦</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day15 开普敦/约堡/香港参考航班：SA332 MO07JUL CPTJNB 1200 1400；SA286 MO07JUL JNBHKG 1655 1225+1</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Day16 7月8日香港</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">@出行准备:</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">①　早晚：5-10度左右，白天：20-25度左右，早晚温差大，在纳米出海比较冷，要穿厚外套。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">②　女性不要穿高根鞋，特别是出海，会不让登船。鞋子应以便鞋和波鞋为好。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">③　常用药品，如感冒，发烧，腹泻，防蚊液等等。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">④　由于阳光紫外线较强，请带足防晒护肤品，遮阳帽，遮阳伞等等</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">⑤　特别强调：要带驱蚊药或者防蚊水，每天擦拭，尽量长衣长裤出门，以防蚊虫叮咬。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">⑥　携带雨具，另外请带多些保鲜袋或者是塑料袋子，在瀑布城拍照时可以派上用场，费事水大损坏相机。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">⑦　晚上不要单独出门，集体活动由导游带领为好。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">⑧　所携带美金需2000年后的美金才可使用，另外请携带多些1美元的零钱，随手小费都是1美金，付小费时方便使用。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">⑨　电压220/240伏，纳米比亚以及<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/southafrica100049.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1892110_100049_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"100049\" data-id=\"58751\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">南非</a>的转换器：南非标（圆形大三孔,小三孔不行），津巴布韦转换器：英标（英式三扁脚）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">⑩　可以携带些饼干，巧克力等小零食，去到当地辛巴红泥人部落后按导游安排派发给当地的小孩。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">11　自备酒店小三样，牙膏、牙刷、拖鞋。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">@特别注意事项：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">飞津巴布韦航班，都没有直达，必须中转，较方便是在南非第一大机场约翰内斯堡中转。但是，订机票时，最好是同一家航空公司的联程机票，否则，就像我们一样，手续繁多。搭乘SA航空抵达约堡后，排队过南非移民关口，重新拿行李，过海关后，上机场二楼到BA航空柜台，接着办第二程登机牌，再拖一次行李。如果是联程机票，下飞机后，直接在移民关口前面的国际中转区，中转，行李直挂，登机牌不需要重办。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong>【比较少登录携程网站，更多不懂的攻略细节，可以加个人微信:604597114,备注-询问纳米比亚，希望可以帮到更多的你们】</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">一、津巴布韦：壮观瀑布和古老文明合一</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">【关于津巴布韦】</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">在非洲西南部，北是赞比亚，南是南非。19世纪末被英国殖民过，曾经也是非洲经济最发达的国家之一，当时人均GDP达到2100美元。但因为独立后，新土地政策计划大规模征收白人商业农场，来安置无地或少地农民，引起了西方国家强烈抵制并给予经济制裁，所以经济大幅下滑，汇率大跌，通胀严重，失业率急升。2003年GDP像维多利亚大瀑布一样，一落千丈，降到359美元，直到近几年才有所缓和。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img16413510\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"16413510|1892110\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"16413510\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"16413510|5510503\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/698/574/388/6714bb08b0674135a1a73427c40e073e_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/698/574/388/6714bb08b0674135a1a73427c40e073e_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/698/574/388/6714bb08b0674135a1a73427c40e073e_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">（1百万大钞，当年大膨胀的产物）<br/>就像一个吴哥窟足以带动整个<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/cambodia100081.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1892110_100081_l\" data-classtype=\"0\" data-resourceid=\"100081\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"9\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">柬埔寨旅游</a>生意一样，<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/victoriafalls20092/123078.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1892110_20092_sii123078_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"123078\" data-id=\"92848\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">维多利亚瀑布</a>支撑着整个国家的旅游业，几乎世界各地游客都是慕名这个大瀑布而来，我们也不例外。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img16414188\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"16414188|1892110\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"16414188\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"16414188|5510503\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/711/915/230/57abbc66d0364f44a9c526745b134ecd_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/711/915/230/57abbc66d0364f44a9c526745b134ecd_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://