n: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">维多利亚大瀑布是非洲第一、世界第二大瀑布【第一大是美加之间的尼亚加拉瀑布】。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">本来是赞比西河中一段平缓的河流，但前进路上突然有个深谷，河水忽然掉入120米大坑，于是排山倒海般地咆哮，无奈深谷不大，一下容纳不了每秒1400立方米的水流量。于是深谷像沸腾的大锅，溅起高高的水雾，以致我们远在十几公里看到，瀑布上方24小时，都有一团像后后白云的水雾。</p><p><br/></p>', '26', '6', '1,2', '2019-05-29', '2019-06-02T19:09:16+', '已发布', '\\uploads\\1559473747106-CggYslcphLaADIF-AAEvoeUvHMk881_C_210_140.jpg', '气势磅礴落差120米的瀑布，温柔安静的草原动物，壮阔巨浪的大西洋，\r\n\r\n惊艳神秘的古老沙漠，，头顶繁星闪烁的银河，神奇的沙海交响，终生不洗澡的辛巴红泥人；\r\n\r\n艳红、暗红、深邃蓝、棕色黄、纯净白、清雅灰、顺滑黑的鲜活色彩，\r\n\r\n这些画面，是一辈子也不会忘怀的人生回忆。', '1677', '3', '2');
INSERT INTO `ys_article` VALUES ('23', '愿时光停留在这里—— 夏威夷13日蜜月行', '<p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">定了将近两周的旅行时间后，也从在旅行社工作的姐姐那被说夏威夷一周就很够了，没什么好玩的，就和马代差不多的看海，泡泳池，天天发呆~后来开始看夏威夷的各种攻略、游记，看了老公定的行程后，开始觉得时间其实一点不够啊，夏威夷原来有8个岛，岛与岛之间必须坐飞机，而我们要好好的深入玩起，这些天最多3个岛，不过这次夏威夷之旅真的是非常非常开心，夏威夷拥有的城市、人文、大海、火山、草原等等等，真的感觉囊括了世界各地的美（除了沙漠哟）~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">　　每个人心目中都有一个夏威夷，而我心目中的夏威夷是自由、浪漫、时而热情奔放，时而温婉恬静，时而伟大壮阔，时而美丽醉人，它真的就是我心目中千变万化的仙境传说~真的超爱这里，每次看到新的景色都被美到心坎里～而这次旅行唯一的遗憾是本来定的倒数第二天重重头戏跳伞因为最后两天<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/hawaii251/66205.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1739878_251_sii66205_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"66205\" data-id=\"88215\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">欧胡岛</a>连着下雨而无缘感受~下次要把跳伞和水上冲击波通通拿下！前言就说了那么多，是因为实在有千言万语述不尽啊，总之夏威夷是人生旅行中决不能错过的一站！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">　　当然我们很高兴在阅览这篇游记的你点开了我们的呕心沥血之作，希望给即将要去或未来准备去的你们带来帮助。　Ａｌｏｈａ！　Ｗｅｌｃｏｍｅ　ｔｏ　Ｈａｗａｉｉ～</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">在亲们开始浏览老公啰嗦的流水账前，先放上一些亮点照片吧~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">同时也建议大家用电脑版阅览更方便快捷，手机版刷图太累也无法欣赏原图哦~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img11816151\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"11816151|1739878\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"11816151\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"11816151|3119865\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/304/825/157/c2c8410a9f67499b8ab144a58a8840c5_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/304/825/157/c2c8410a9f67499b8ab144a58a8840c5_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/304/825/157/c2c8410a9f67499b8ab144a58a8840c5_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">摄于2014年2月12日<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/hawaii251/66282.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1739878_251_sii66282_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"66282\" data-id=\"88246\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">茂宜岛</a>，参加了Pacific Whale Fundation组织的Whale Photo Safari。身边的拍鲸专家说，这张照片可以刊登在当地的海报上来，可把老公美的，哈哈~~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">拍摄难点：茫茫大海中，鲸鱼可能出现在任何位置（船上用1点-12点来沟通方位，有人发现目标就报方位，然后大家一拥而上。）鲸鱼跃出水面也就几秒钟，而你需要有肉眼发现、移动相机、对焦、按下快门等多个步骤，因此拍到躯干、尾巴照片的居多，头部跃起照片较少。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">拍鲸窍门（由旁边的专家告知）：快门优先（S档），1/250秒，ISO 400，连拍模式。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">老公拍鲸前，预先也做了很久的熟练度测试。就是用最快的速度将目标纳入倒取景框中。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">相机的对焦速度也需要足够快，否则会经常出现按不下快门的情况。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">老公用的是尼康D7000，套机头（18-200），镜头有超声波自动对焦马达，机身防抖。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">三脚架不需要带，木有用的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img11815765\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"11815765|1739878\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"11815765\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"11815765|3119865\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/703/004/319/6a800e4f8e00414489c1181eb86ab1ee_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/703/004/319/6a800e4f8e00414489c1181eb86ab1ee_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/703/004/319/6a800e4f8e00414489c1181eb86ab1ee_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">摄于2014年2月10日<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/hawaii251/66279.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1739878_251_sii66279_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"66279\" data-id=\"88244\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">大岛</a><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/hawaii251/137502.html\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"137502\" data-id=\"98812\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">Mauna Kea</a>（必须得点开看大图哦，不一样的感受，还能看到射电光束和偷偷躲藏的阳光）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">拍这张照片的前一天，老公三脚架的快装板不小心丢了。这个重重的三脚架，跟了我们7000公里来到夏威夷，却在最关键的时候掉链子。。。在拍摄当天，老公和阿吉（在大岛同甘共苦的朋友）灵机一动，直接把相机架倒了岩石上，利用岩石的不规则边缘来调整角度。然后用遥控快门线按快门，才获得这一系列照片。当晚，我们是Mauna Kea最后下山的一辆车。老公很粗心在拍摄中，车钥匙不小心掉了，幸好后来被阿吉夫妇发现，否则一个晚上后大家就成为一堆冰棍了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">光圈最大，对焦无限远，色温2550k，ISO 1000</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img11816098\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"11816098|1739878\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"11816098\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"11816098|3119865\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/472/322/958/b50b29d4d74d4bf2ab6bfde0d312a46e_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/472/322/958/b50b29d4d74d4bf2ab6bfde0d312a46e_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/472/322/958/b50b29d4d74d4bf2ab6bfde0d312a46e_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9