il家便只停留了4个景点拍照。（游记底部有短视频链接~）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">夏威夷哈纳公路(<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/hana19136.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1739878_19136_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"19136\" data-id=\"17613\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">Hana</a>&nbsp;Highway)贯穿茂伊岛北部海岸，经常被视为世界上路边风景最为优美的公路之一。哈纳公路全长52英里(约合84公里)，共有大约600个弯道，经过54座桥梁(大多数是单行道)。哈纳公路蜿蜒曲折的路面狭窄，路边景色优美，驾车者往往要花4小时才能通过。（来自百度百科介绍）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><div id=\"img11816104\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"11816104|1739878\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"11816104\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"11816104|3119865\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/254/776/686/f5a69ddc285b48ebad855e504ed653b9_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/254/776/686/f5a69ddc285b48ebad855e504ed653b9_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/254/776/686/f5a69ddc285b48ebad855e504ed653b9_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">黄昏的<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/waikiki141153.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1739878_141153_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"141153\" data-id=\"75486\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">Waikiki</a>&nbsp;Beach——夏威夷最经典的标志性度假海滩</p><p><br/></p>', '12', '3', '2,3,4', '2019-06-02', '2019-06-02T12:16:10+', '已发布', '\\uploads\\1559448946938-c2c8410a9f67499b8ab144a58a8840c5_C_210_140.jpg', '　刚决定蜜月要去夏威夷时，本是要定朋友旅行社的6日5晚的半自助游旅行，幸好老公后来无意间看到微博上携程的特价机票，于是峰回路转定了13日游的自由行程，后来也是从先前的犹豫不定到最后感叹这是一次最对的决定！！！', '228', '3', '2');
INSERT INTO `ys_article` VALUES ('24', '春游安徽｜解锁一趟寻忆之旅', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">壮丽旖旎的黄山，水墨韵味的宏村……安徽在我的眼中，一直以来都是风光秀丽之地。但之前对安徽的了解，大多是在自然景观上。可事实上，安徽颇具文化底蕴的景点，也有不少。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">这一次，与以往的安徽行不大相同，旅行线路中涉及到的景点，多是与文化相关。为了贴合清明节的气氛，还特别去到了<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/fengyang2626/17521.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3796022_2626_sid17521_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"17521\" data-id=\"79694\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">明皇陵</a>和李白墓，可以说是主题性很强的一次旅行了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">如果你像我一样，想要在感受春天的同时，又品读历史，那么就去安徽，解锁一趟寻忆之旅吧！清明节假期已经过去了，五一还会远吗？赶紧计划起来吧！</p><h5 class=\"title5\" id=\"89430193\" style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 25px; font-size: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 30px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">行程安排</h5><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">DAY1&nbsp;南昌→<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/hefei196.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3796022_196_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"196\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">合肥</a>→滨湖湿地国家森林公园→<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/chuzhou228.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3796022_228_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"228\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">滁州</a><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/fengyang2626.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3796022_2626_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"2626\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">凤阳</a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">DAY2&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/fengyang2626/62799.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3796022_2626_sid62799_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"62799\" data-id=\"87244\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">明中都皇城遗址</a>→<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/fengyang2626/17521.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3796022_2626_sid17521_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"17521\" data-id=\"79694\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">明皇陵</a>→<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/chuzhou228/55559.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3796022_228_sid55559_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"55559\" data-id=\"85402\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">琅琊山</a>→<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/maanshan503.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3796022_503_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"503\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">马鞍山</a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">DAY3&nbsp;濮塘国家度假公园→李白墓→<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/dangtu1445969.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3796022_1445969_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"1445969\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">当涂</a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">DAY4&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/dangtu1445969.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3796022_1445969_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"1445969\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51