INSERT INTO `ys_article` VALUES ('25', '慢行中欧，谱一曲中世纪的浪漫童话', '<p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">想去布拉格，想去欧洲，那些诗词歌句，电影电视里常常惊艳出场的红屋顶，应该是很多人这辈子都心心念念要去打卡的地方吧；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">或许是蔡依林的那首《布拉格广场》，即使没有布拉格广场和许愿池，即使那时候喜欢的偶像cp最终没有走在一起，布拉格依然是许多人心底最甜蜜柔软的一处地方，有着旧时年少最美的期待；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">或许是徐静蕾的文艺气质，自导自演的那部《有一个地方只有我们知道》，沉迷于男女主的颜值中无法自拔的同时，也被奶奶和医生的忘年之念深深打动，在那样一个唯美浪漫的地方酝酿的爱情也更加深情缱绻，有着曾经沧海最真的等待；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">或许是自幼爱听歌爱看书看电影，翻着那些关乎布拉格的故事，目光所及的每一个细节都传递着久远的讯息，嗅着<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/prague822/134157.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_3810204_822_sii134157_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"134157\" data-id=\"96069\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">伏尔塔瓦河</a>上飘过的皮尔森酒香，仿佛时间已然停滞，似乎转过这个街口，你就会遇见故事中的人物，从《变形记》里进入到属于他创造的梦幻世界。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">一路从杭州出发，登上转机阿姆斯特丹的荷兰航空，四只许久未见的小伙伴仍然兴奋不已，叽叽喳喳怼个不停，上了飞机几只漫威迷愣是把美队，钢铁侠，黑豹，死侍，复联又重新回味了一遍；</p><div id=\"img320600481\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"320600481|3810204\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"320600481\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"320600481|89748848\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blan