t: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">世界如果是一个国家，那首都一定是<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/istanbul258.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3754812_258_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"258\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">伊斯坦布尔</a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">在这个亚欧交界之地，不知道经历了多少风霜雨雪</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">而即便是在卓然不群的<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/istanbul258.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3754812_258_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"258\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">伊斯坦布尔</a>，圣索非亚大教堂依然没有能超越它的建筑。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">在曾经的数百年光阴里，它一直都是基督世界最伟大的教堂。</p><div class=\"img\" id=\"img298363390\" data-likeid=\"298363390|3754812\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"298363390\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"298363390|5102507\" data-refe