-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">就好像穿越回了曾经的奥斯曼帝国一般</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">在这里</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">时间好像是静止的一般……</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">记得来之前看过一部老片，成龙主演的《特务迷城》</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">这部片子的大部分镜头都是在<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/turkey100073.html#ctm_ref=gs_290606_3754812_100073_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"100073\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); padding-bottom: 2px;\">土耳其</a>拍的</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">少说也