INSERT INTO `ys_article` VALUES ('28', '突然想去看海--南半球的初春', '<p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong>出行前准备</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong>1、签证</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">官网 http://www.china.embassy.gov.au/bjngchinese/DIAC07092012p1cn.html 签证需要的表格、资料和签证费都可以在官网找到。澳签是电子签证，在护照上没有签证贴签（以后翻开护照本，就看不到满满的不同花色的签证了，可惜贴个标签要另外花好几百，这个性价比太低了）。澳签不太容易被拒，签出后大多都是一年多次往返，还有一点好，就是不用面签，但有时会电调，不过我这次没有碰到，5-6个工作日就拿到了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/><strong>2、机票</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">国际段：上海 --&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/sydney236.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1580978_236_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"236\" data-id=\"152\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">悉尼</a>澳航直飞，来回含税5513RMB一人。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">澳洲国内段：悉尼 --&gt;&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/goldcoast456/122816.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1580978_456_sii122816_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"122816\" data-id=\"92643\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">黄金海岸</a>&nbsp;<br/>VIRGIN航空</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/brisbane323.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_1580978_323_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"323\" data-id=\"218\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">布里斯班</a>&nbsp;--&gt; Proserpine&nbsp;<br/>VIRGIN航空</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Hamilton --&gt; 悉尼&nbsp;<br/>JETSTAR航空</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">澳洲国内的廉价航空主要是VIRGIN、JETSTAR和TIGER，TIGER最便宜，但口碑不太好，出门在外还是保险点，所以虎航就不在考虑范围了，VIRGIN和JETSTAR经常会搞特价。推荐个澳洲机票价格的比较网站 http://iwantthatflight.com.au&nbsp;<br/>。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/><strong>3、住宿</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">黄金海岸</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">ONE THE&nbsp;<br/>ESPLANADE （<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://hotels.ctrip.com/international/2855071.html\" data-classtype=\"0\" data-resourceid=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"97\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">http://hotels.ctrip.com/international/2855071.html</a>&nbsp;） 3晚600AUD</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">大堡礁</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Airlie&nbsp;<br/>Waterfront（<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://hotels.ctrip.com/international/739505.html\" data-classtype=\"0\" data-resourceid=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"97\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">http://hotels.ctrip.com/international/739505.html</a>&nbsp;） 3晚636AUD</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">悉尼</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">MERITON PITT&nbsp;<br/>STREET（<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://hotels.ctrip.com/international/1889173.html\" data-classtype=\"0\" data-resourceid=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-type=\"97\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 134, 180); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 134, 180); padding-bottom: 2px;\">http://hotels.ctrip.com/international/1889173.html</a>&nbsp;）&nbsp;<br/>2晚351AUD</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">当初比较了N家，这三家真心不算便宜，幸好都算贵的值得，稍后游记容我慢慢道来。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/><strong>4、电话卡</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">OPTUS 2AUD/天套餐：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">无限次拨打澳洲境内电话和手机，无限制收发澳洲境内短讯，无限制3G上网一路经过的地方3G信号都很好，当然出海除外。因为订的游玩项目都要做电话check-in，办张电话卡确实方便很多，关键还能随时google地图，晚上方向感不好的时候太有用了。<br/><br/>澳洲之行留下了很多美好的回忆，无论是那里的景色还是当地的居民，当然最喜欢的还是Airlie&nbsp;<br/>小镇，作为游玩大堡礁的主要门户之一，很难得的保持了原有的生活环境，没有被过度商业化；而悉尼的城市太像上海，没有太多惊喜，人们当然也没小镇上来得淳朴热情；黄金海岸那绵延四十多公里的海滩，随意漫步就好，这才是度假的乐趣。记录的文字和照片，始终不及亲眼所见来得动人，或许，这也是旅行的意义吧。</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/>游记正式开始啦</p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><strong>9.12 上海浦东 --&gt; 悉尼</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><br/>10小时的长途飞行，终于告别漆黑的夜空，迎来了美丽的朝阳。</p><div id=\"img83645431\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"83645431|1580978\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"83645431\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" 