ps://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1001090000003szl48419_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1001090000003szl48419_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/></p><div id=\"img83646499\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"83646499|1580978\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"83646499\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"83646499|1976354\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100p090000003szim7D8E_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100p090000003szim7D8E_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100p090000003szim7D8E_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/></p><div id=\"img83645730\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"83645730|1580978\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"83645730\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"83645730|1976354\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100o090000003szknF32E_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100o090000003szknF32E_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100o090000003szknF32E_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">飞机准时降落在悉尼机场，两小时的时差，身体几乎感觉不到差异。澳洲入关很严格，但没有想象中那么麻烦，事先申报了携带药品，就被问了句“medicine?”，没开箱就直接放行了（他们对别人的信任，在这次旅行中深深感受到了这点，这种信任让我也很愿意去相信他们）来到机场大厅，很容易就找到OPTUS的黄色招牌，办了10天套餐，花了20AUD（他们会负责帮你装卡激活，所以直接使用就可以了）</span></p><div id=\"img83646885\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"83646885|1580978\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"83646885\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"83646885|1976354\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100r090000003szjvB00B_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100r090000003szjvB00B_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100r090000003szjvB00B_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">悉尼机场也分国际T1和国内T2T3，跟着路标走，就能找到通往T2的TRAIN或者T-bus的所在。好有爱的广告灯箱。</span></p><div id=\"img83646500\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"83646500|1580978\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"83646500\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"83646500|1976354\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1002090000003szl840E0_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1002090000003szl840E0_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1002090000003szl840E0_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">T1到T2，5AUD一人</span></p><div id=\"img83646975\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"83646975|1580978\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"83646975\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"83646975|1976354\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1007090000003szmu5ADF_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1007090000003szmu5ADF_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1007090000003szmu5ADF_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">T2里可吃可逛的店也不少。来到澳洲的第一顿就是它了，PIE FACE（样子蛮诱人的，就是吃起来咸的太咸，甜的太甜）</span></p><div id=\"img83646806\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"83646806|1580978\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"83646806\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"83646806|1976354\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100r090000003szjwA02A_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100r090000003szjwA02A_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/100r090000003szjwA02A_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"/></p><div id=\"img83647733\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"83647733|1580978\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"83647733\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"83647733|1976354\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; background-image: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/ctd_img_bg.png?t=f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;); position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 790px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STXihei, simsun, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1008090000003szoz9AC4_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 167, 225);\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1008090000003szoz9AC4_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" src=\"https://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/1008090000003szoz9AC4_R_671_10000_Q90.jpg?proc=autoorient\" width=\"671\" style=\"border-style: initial; display: block; max-width: 670px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; background: url(&quot;//pages.c-ctrip.com/gs_static/travels/img/img_loading.gif?t=127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;) center center no-repeat;\"/></a></div><p><br/></p>', '11', '5', '1,2,3,4', '2019-06-02', null, '已发布', '\\uploads\\1559478075029-100u090000003szsoB4B9_C_210_140.jpg', '突然想去看海，也许是怀念起海浪冲刷着沙滩的声音，也许是想念着细软沙子滑过脚趾的感觉，也许是爱上了阳光下波光粼粼的海面，又或许只是因为那无边无际、深深浅浅绵延到天际的蓝色......凡此种种，对大堡礁的向往，来得愈发强烈。于是我从北半球的夏末，飞去南半球的初春。在这片环海的大陆，一路北上，去寻找心中的那片海。', '1', '0', '2');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('1', '请问丽江三月份穿衣指南', '请问3月20号左右到丽江随后到大理 一些穿衣指南 需要带什么必需品？', '3', '2019-02-01', '1', '8');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('2', '3、4月份台北，台中的天气', '大概3月底去台北还有台中，想知道那边大概的天气情况', '1', '2019-02-11', '1', '9');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('3', '有关三圣乡问题，麻烦达人解惑', '麻烦求教一下：我想去三圣乡逛逛、拍拍照片。在网上看到有许多不错的景色，不知道具体地址是什么地方，比如是去白鹭湿地公园还是华博路这？或是到荷塘月色这？还有据说最近有绣球花在展览，有达人知道是在什么地方吗？', '14', '2019-03-23', '1', '21');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('4', '登泰山观日峰需要几个小时？', '亲们朋友们，登泰山需要几个小时啊？登观日峰，想看日出，提前几个小时登山比较好？', '17', '2019-04-04', '1', '6');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('5', '内蒙古游玩7天，走哪条线比较好？一条是呼和浩特，一条是呼伦贝尔', '20人7月中旬从湖南去内蒙古，大约去7天左右，是去呼和浩特还是呼伦贝尔好呢？', '25', '2019-05-05', '1', '4');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('6', '打算8月去青海湖，茶卡盐湖，敦煌等4天的行程，想求助一下旅行路线和租车方式？', '打算是在8月份去那边游玩，暂时是打算到西宁机场，从西宁出发，总共差不多是4天的行程，比较想去的就是青海湖、茶卡盐湖、敦煌等，最好是可以推荐合理的路线和住宿的酒店以及租车的一些方式，谢谢了！', '26', '2019-05-14', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('7', '买了钟山风景区门票 中山陵还需网上预约么', '是不是买了100的门票 中山陵不需预约', '26', '2019-05-14', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('8', '五月份出游 哪里比较好呢？', '五月中旬左右吧   大概七八天的时间   去哪里走走比较好？   注 ：穷游', '25', '2019-05-14', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('14', '请问三天时间带老人孩子去西安游玩兵马俑，大雁塔，陕西博物馆，永兴坊或者回民街，怎么住玩？谢谢', '请问三天时间带老人孩子去西安游玩兵马俑，大雁塔，陕西博物馆，永兴坊或者回民街，怎么住玩？谢谢', '13', '2019-06-01', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('15', '两人在长沙，想去凤凰古城，张家界玩，长沙也没玩过， 我们是自由行，还是跟团游，10天时间', ' 想在长沙玩一天到两天，我们是自己坐车去凤凰古城玩，玩完在坐车去张家界找当地团游玩张家界，还是直接在长沙报团，游玩凤凰古城，张家界，那种实惠又能玩好，谢谢回复，', '18', '2019-06-02', '1', '2');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('17', '6月初大草原草原风景怎么样', '过几天想去大草原看看，6月初大草原草原风景怎么样', '28', '2019-06-02', '1', '5');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('16', '端午节三天时间 参观故宫 天安门等 这样安排时间排的开嘛', '第一天：12点左右到北京站，然后坐地铁去天安门，然后故宫，然后去欢乐谷夜场，住在欢乐谷附近。\r\n第二天：6点半出门，去圆明园，然后颐和园，去三庆园看2点午场的相声，4点结束 去鸟巢水立方看夜景，结束后回焦化厂。\r\n第三天：从焦化厂去南锣鼓巷，然后去中央戏剧学院外边看看，坐地铁回北京站，大约下午2点的火车。\r\n求指教，可以赶的开嘛，端午节的时候去。', '28', '2019-06-02', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('18', '大理。苍山洱海现在能去旅游了吗？', '计划六月份去大理苍山洱海玩几天，可听说洱海周边客栈饭店都停业整顿了，没有好的海景房住宿。是真的吗？', '26', '2019-06-02', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `ys_ask` VALUES ('19', '泰山白天爬好还是晚上', '请问泰山白天去爬好还是晚上去爬好', '16', '2019-06-02', '1', '2');
